Module fi.tuni.progthree.weatherapp
Package fi.tuni.prog3.weatherapp.Model

Class WeatherItem

java.lang.Object
fi.tuni.prog3.weatherapp.Model.WeatherItem
public class WeatherItem extends Object
Represents a generic weather item with basic information. This class can be extended or used as a base class for more specific weather-related objects.
